ABBREVIATIONS
OFF - Offense; Team in Possession
DEF - Defense; Team NOT in Possession
KO - Kickoff
HC - Head Coach
OC - Offensive Coordinator
DC - Defensive Coordinator
PB - Playbook
QB - Quarterback
RB - Running Back
WR - Wide Receiver
TE - Tight End
OL - Offensive Line
DL - Defensive Line
LB - Linebacker
S - Safety (Player)
CB - Cornerback
K - Kicker
P - Punter
RET - Returner
TO - Timeout
TD - Touchdown
FG - Field Goal
XP - Extra Point
2P - 2-point Conversion
SAF - Safety (scoring play when Offensive player is tackled in their own Endzone)
MEZ - My Endzone
Z1 - Build Zone
Z2 - Advance Zone
Z3 - Midfield Zone
Z4 - Attacking Zone
Z5 - Red Zone
EZ - Endzone
FUM - Fumble
INT - Interception
SUB - Substitution (When a team removes a player from the team on the field and puts in another player from the Player Bench)
